Introduction

Jang Eunbi is a South Korean singer and a former member of Daydream, which was under Girls Frontier. She graduated from the group on September 8, 2024. She is known for her captivating visuals and sweet vocals leading her to rank 2nd in the August Individual Rankings. In addition to her musical career, Eunbi showcased her talents on the web show Super Girls Battle in 2023 and she is set to appear in the visual novel game "Five Hearts Under One Roof" developed by 3YCorporation's MilkFilm. Having cheerleading experience for four years, her fanbase is called Eunbidan.
